OL,3,CMan to serve at least 32 years behind
OL,4,Cbars for murdering mother-of-seven
OL,6,FA man who murdered a mother-of-seven
OL,7,Fin a violent sex attack has been told
OL,8,Fhe must serve at least 32 years behind
OL,9,Fbars.
OL,11,FPaul Irwin, 50, was high on cocaine
OL,12,Fand had been drinking lager before
OL,13,Fkilling 34-year-old Tiffany Render at
OL,14,Fhis flat on 22 March.
OL,16,FCarlisle Crown Court heard how, at
OL,17,Fthat time, Irwin was subject to a
OL,18,Fsuspended jail term for previous
OL,19,Fdomestic violence against Miss Render.
