OL,6,FLast July, he had struck her
OL,7,Frepeatedly with a heavy wooden rolling
OL,8,Fpin, also slapping and strangling her.
OL,10,FWeeks before his attack, Irwin was
OL,11,Ftwice arrested, bailed and banned from
OL,12,Fcontacting Miss Render for other
OL,13,Falleged abuse as he exercised full
OL,14,Fcontrol over her life.
OL,16,FIn late February she told police Irwin
OL,17,Fhad kicked her after sinking 18 beers
OL,18,Fas she lay outside his property in the
OL,19,Fdead of night.
