OL,6,FOn 4 March, Miss Render reported Irwin
OL,7,Frepeatedly threatening her by phone
OL,8,Fwhile drunk. Officer bodycam footage
OL,9,Fcaptured her on a call with Irwin, and
OL,10,Freporting his vows to "batter" and
OL,11,Fknock her out.
OL,13,FDays later she obtained safe
OL,14,Faccommodation but ` despite Irwin's
OL,15,Fbail conditions ` continued to stay at
OL,16,Fhis flat in Whitehaven, which she
OL,17,Fvisited on 22 March.
