OL,6,FJust before midnight, Irwin called 999
OL,7,Fand said he believed Miss Render was
OL,8,Fdead. Paramedics attended and found
OL,9,Fher unresponsive, surrounded by blood-
OL,10,Fsoaked bedding. She was pronounced
OL,11,Fdead by a doctor.
OL,13,F"The severe force which caused the
OL,14,Finjury led to almost immediate
OL,15,Fbleeding and Miss Render bled to death
OL,16,Finside this defendant's home," said
OL,17,FIain Simkin KC, prosecuting.
