OL,6,FA Home Office pathologist concluded
OL,7,Fthat pouring blood loss from a
OL,8,Fterrible injury would have led to her
OL,9,Fcollapsing within 20 minutes and death
OL,10,Finside an hour at the latest. She died
OL,11,Ffrom a haemorrhage.
OL,13,FIrwin, of George Street, Whitehaven,
OL,14,Fdenied murder but was convicted,
OL,15,Funanimously, by a jury who heard
OL,16,Fevidence of his violence.
OL,18,FHe was sentenced on Tuesday having
OL,19,Falso admitted sexual assaulting her.
