OL,6,F"She was without doubt, an extremely
OL,7,Fvulnerable woman who was emotionally
OL,8,Fand psychologically trapped inside an
OL,9,Faggressive, violent and controlling
OL,10,Frelationship," said Mr Simkin, "and it
OL,11,Fwas against that background that this
OL,12,Fdefendant murdered her."
OL,14,FIn one text to Irwin, Miss Render had
OL,15,Fsaid: "If you did love me, you
OL,16,Fwouldn't hurt me again and again and
OL,17,Fagain."
