OL,6,FImpact statements revealed she was a
OL,7,Fmother to seven children cared for by
OL,8,Fher family; also a sister, a loving
OL,9,Fauntie, a niece and a cousin.
OL,11,F"The heartbreak is unbearable," stated
OL,12,Fher mother, Hazel Marginson. "No
OL,13,Fparent should ever have to go through
OL,14,Fthis. No parent should ever have to
OL,15,Fbury a child. This will haunt me for
OL,16,Fthe rest of my life. I am a changed
OL,17,Fwoman forever."
