OL,6,FOne of Miss Render's sisters,
OL,7,FCaroline, called the impact on their
OL,8,Ffamily "devastating", saying of Irwin:
OL,9,F"Tiffany's caring nature shone through
OL,10,Funtil his cowardly behaviour took her
OL,11,Flife from us." Caroline added:
OL,12,F"Tiffany had a heart of gold."
OL,14,FAnother sister, Gemma, said: "The
OL,15,Factions and consequences of the
OL,16,Fdefendant's actions have wreaked havoc
OL,17,Fthrough our entire family. The sudden
OL,18,Fand tragic loss of our Tiffany is
OL,19,Fsomething that as a family will haunt
OL,20,Fus forever more."
