OL,6,FGemma added: "Mr Irwin, by his
OL,7,Fdespicable actions and selfish,
OL,8,Fjealous behaviour has given our family
OL,9,Fa life sentence of sadness and trauma.
OL,10,FTiffany was a bright, bubbly, clever
OL,11,Fand oh-so-loving person. We will miss
OL,12,Fher massively for the rest of our
OL,13,Flives."
OL,15,FPeter Glenser KC, mitigating for
OL,16,FIrwin, said: "He didn't intend to kill
OL,17,Fher. He is truly remorseful."
