OL,6,FMrs Justice Foster accepted it had not
OL,7,Fbeen a pre-planned attack. The judge
OL,8,Fimposed a mandatory life sentence,
OL,9,Fruling that Irwin should serve a
OL,10,Fminimum of 32 years in prison before
OL,11,Fbeing considered for parole.
OL,13,F"She was an extremely vulnerable woman
OL,14,Fand your treatment of her increased
OL,15,Fthat vulnerability," Mrs Justice
OL,16,FFoster told Irwin. "Your history of
OL,17,Fattacks while drunk reveals a cycle of
OL,18,Falcohol, violence, regret."
