OL,6,FThe judge added: "Her appalling
OL,7,Finjuries were caused by your actions.
OL,8,FOnly you know the full detail of what
OL,9,Fhappened in that flat."
OL,11,FIrwin must sign the sex offenders'
OL,12,Fregister for life.
OL,14,FDetective Constable Lisa Baker said:
OL,15,F"I am pleased that Paul Irwin has been
OL,16,Fconvicted of the murder of Tiffany
OL,17,FRender and that he will now spend a
OL,18,Fsignificant amount of time in prison
OL,19,Ffor what he did.
