OL,6,F"This is a tragic loss of a life, and
OL,7,Fno one should have to suffer at the
OL,8,Fhands of their partner in such a
OL,9,Fhorrific way.
OL,11,F"My thoughts remain with Tiffany's
OL,12,Ffamily and friends at this incredibly
OL,13,Fdifficult time.
OL,15,F"We know that no sentence passed will
OL,16,Fbe able to bring Tiffany back, but I
OL,17,Fdo hope that the sentence passed today
OL,18,Fcan go some way in giving them some
OL,19,Fsort of closure knowing that Irwin is
OL,20,Fnow behind bars for what he did to
OL,21,FTiffany."
